# Frontend Standards

## Vue 3 Patterns
- Always use `<script setup>` Composition API
- Use Pinia stores for global state (query, reports, auth)
- Use `composables/` for reusable logic (useChart, useQuery)

## Drivee Brand Colors in Tailwind
- Primary: `green-500` (#2ECC71), `green-700` (#1A7A42)
- Background: `green-50` (#F0FDF4)
- Text: `gray-900`
- Danger: `red-500`
- Warning: `yellow-500`
- Use gradient: `from-green-600 to-green-400`

## Key Components
- `ChatInterface.vue` — main query input + response area
- `ThinkingLog.vue` — expandable AI reasoning panel (always visible)
- `ChartRenderer.vue` — Chart.js with auto chart type selection
- `DataTable.vue` — sortable table with column toggle
- `SecurityPanel.vue` — guardrail status, role display

## Chart Auto-Selection Logic
- Time series data → Line chart
- Category comparisons → Bar chart  
- Part-of-whole → Pie/Doughnut chart
- Single metric → KPI card
- Always offer toggle between chart ↔ table view

## ThinkingLog Display
- Show AI reasoning in collapsible panel below query
- Style with `border-l-4 border-yellow-400 bg-yellow-50 text-xs font-mono`
- Label: "🤔 Как я понял запрос" / "🧠 Размышления ИИ"

## API Base URL
- Use `VITE_API_URL` env var, default `http://localhost:8000`
